Director Zhou would like to invite you over

575
00:33:44,110 --> 00:33:46,810
for a cup of tea and a catch-up.

576
00:33:52,610 --> 00:33:56,750
[Zhaowen Hotel]

577
00:33:53,450 --> 00:33:54,520
Don't look!

578
00:33:54,870 --> 00:33:55,790
Go away!

579
00:33:55,790 --> 00:33:56,450
Let go of me!

580
00:33:57,030 --> 00:33:57,870
Stop looking!

581
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,340
I'm a businessman!

582
00:33:59,370 --> 00:34:00,790
What gives you the right to arrest me?

583
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:02,030
I'm just a businessman!

584
00:34:02,030 --> 00:34:02,630
Shut up!

585
00:34:03,070 --> 00:34:05,630
A businessman? You know exactly

586
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:06,630
who you are.

587
00:34:06,900 --> 00:34:07,700
Take him away!

588
00:34:08,949 --> 00:34:09,860
Let go of me!

589
00:34:27,860 --> 00:34:29,870
[A Collection of Famous Suzhou Poems Across the Ages]

590
00:34:30,770 --> 00:34:35,980
Do you not see the Yellow River come from the sky,

591
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:38,550
[A Collection of Wang Tong's Poems]

592
00:34:36,750 --> 00:34:40,400
rushing into the sea and never come back?

593
00:34:41,909 --> 00:34:46,900
Do you not see the mirrors bright in chambers high,

594
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:49,219
grieve over your snow-white hair...

595
00:35:01,250 --> 00:35:01,870
Say it!

596
00:35:02,700 --> 00:35:03,620
Are you going to say it or not?

597
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:06,590
I'll let you know what the real No. 90 is!

598
00:35:10,540 --> 00:35:14,260
[A Collection of Famous Suzhou Poems Across the Ages]

599
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:36,030
Comrade Wang Mingzhong has been arrested.

600
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:40,350
According to the rules of the organization,

601
00:35:40,350 --> 00:35:41,390
our team,

602
00:35:41,650 --> 00:35:44,580
as the direct operatives of Comrade Wang Mingzhong,

603
00:35:45,510 --> 00:35:47,110
should immediately cease all activities...

604
00:35:47,110 --> 00:35:48,190
And withdraw.

605
00:35:51,570 --> 00:35:53,500
But I don't want to do that, Junxia.

606
00:35:53,500 --> 00:35:54,420
I suggest

607
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:57,690
we should make every effort to rescue Comrade Mingzhong.

608
00:35:57,690 --> 00:35:58,570
I think the same.

609
00:35:58,570 --> 00:35:59,420
Do you have a plan?

610
00:35:59,420 --> 00:35:59,900
Yes.

611
00:36:00,150 --> 00:36:01,990
I've just telegraphed Director Lin of the Ministry of Political Affairs,

612
00:36:01,990 --> 00:36:02,870
requesting his approval

613
00:36:02,870 --> 00:36:05,800
to implement the rescue plan for Comrade Mingzhong.

614
00:36:11,970 --> 00:36:13,350
Commander, he's here.

615
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:21,390
You know Mr. Lin Guoping?

616
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:25,610
They are my trusted aides.

617
00:36:25,950 --> 00:36:26,480
Speak up.

618
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:32,700
Mr. Lin has a note for you.

619
00:36:37,450 --> 00:36:39,650
[Wu, the one with the note is one of us. Ping]

620
00:36:47,830 --> 00:36:50,000
You work for Mr. Lin?

621
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:51,300
Yes, Commander.

622
00:36:52,310 --> 00:36:53,520
I am Xiao Junxia, a special agent

623
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:57,120
from the Suzhou-Shanghai Liaison Office of the New Fourth Army.

624
00:36:57,590 --> 00:36:58,630
What are you here for?

625
00:36:58,630 --> 00:37:01,310
I'm here to ask for your help in rescuing Wang Mingzhong,

626
00:37:01,310 --> 00:37:02,960
who has been captured

627
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:03,950
by No. 90.

628
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:06,920
Kill him.

629
00:37:07,430 --> 00:37:07,850
I...

630
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:13,510
Zhou Fohai recruited my brothers and me as Armed Police Forces.

631
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,750
Mr. Li

632
00:37:15,430 --> 00:37:17,030
wants to offer us 30 million.

633
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:20,190
What can your New Fourth Army offer

634
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:22,610
in return for our cooperation?

635
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:23,730
Commander,

636
00:37:24,330 --> 00:37:26,670
we can ensure that you and your 8,000 brothers

637
00:37:26,670 --> 00:37:28,670
will live with honor and integrity.

638
00:37:30,640 --> 00:37:32,880
We are already living with honor and integrity.

639
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:33,590
Are you?

640
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:35,340
Nonsense! I'll kill you!

641
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:36,290
Let him finish.

642
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:37,930
Commander Luo,

643
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,290
I know you are a person

644
00:37:39,290 --> 00:37:40,500
of loyalty and righteousness.

645
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:42,190
You treat your soldiers

646
00:37:42,350 --> 00:37:43,360
like family,

647
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:44,530
sharing the same food and living conditions.

648
00:37:44,530 --> 00:37:45,460
As family,

649
00:37:45,630 --> 00:37:46,810
do you want them to carry the stigma of traitors

650
00:37:46,810 --> 00:37:48,810
for the rest of their lives with you?

651
00:37:49,270 --> 00:37:50,410
No matter what the present situation is,

652
00:37:50,410 --> 00:37:51,850
history will always be remembered.

653
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:52,750
In the near future,

654
00:37:52,750 --> 00:37:53,520
traitors

655
00:37:53,550 --> 00:37:55,030
will certainly face the judgment of the people.

656
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:57,190
With the current situation being unpredictable,

657
00:37:57,190 --> 00:37:58,990
how can we talk about the future?

658
00:37:59,070 --> 00:38:00,530
Commander, you are wrong.

659
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:03,110
Across the country, the Communist Party is in the Northwest,

660
00:38:03,110 --> 00:38:04,480
the Kuomintang is in the Southwest,

661
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:06,970
and they are united in resisting the Japanese invaders.

662
00:38:06,970 --> 00:38:07,910
In Jiangsu Province,

663
00:38:07,910 --> 00:38:09,470
the New Fourth Army in Southern Jiangsu

664
00:38:09,470 --> 00:38:11,550
is adhering to the policy of united resistance,

665
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:13,510
and the anti-pacification operation has achieved great success.

666
00:38:13,510 --> 00:38:14,670
In the future, China will certainly

667
00:38:14,670 --> 00:38:17,130
be able to drive away the Japanese invaders.

668
00:38:18,070 --> 00:38:19,470
Take him out and kill him!

669
00:38:19,850 --> 00:38:20,510
-Yes!
-Yes!

670
00:38:20,590 --> 00:38:21,790
The Japanese army is threatening our country...

671
00:38:21,790 --> 00:38:22,150
Get out!

672
00:38:22,150 --> 00:38:23,170
And oppressing our 400 million people!

673
00:38:23,170 --> 00:38:24,430
Our compatriots are crying out and vowing

674
00:38:24,430 --> 00:38:25,340
to defend the motherland with their lives!

675
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:25,740
Don't move!

676
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:26,750
Let alone us, patriotic soldiers

677
00:38:26,750 --> 00:38:28,070
of iron and blood?

678
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:28,970
Commander Luo!

679
00:38:28,990 --> 00:38:30,710
Have you forgotten what your former superior,

680
00:38:30,710 --> 00:38:32,030
General Feng Yuxiang, said?

681
00:38:32,030 --> 00:38:32,710
If he saw

682
00:38:32,710 --> 00:38:33,910
what you have become now,

683
00:38:33,910 --> 00:38:35,820
how heartbroken he would be!

684
00:38:37,140 --> 00:38:38,120
Let go of him.

685
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:44,880
Commander.

686
00:38:48,100 --> 00:38:50,780
Commander, both the Division Commander of our 6th Division

687
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,590
and Commander Chen of the New Fourth Army

688
00:38:52,590 --> 00:38:53,960
hope you will abandon darkness and turn to the light.

689
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:55,110
We'll talk about it later.

690
00:38:55,110 --> 00:38:55,770
Commander!

691
00:38:58,750 --> 00:38:59,590
Come here.

692
00:39:04,350 --> 00:39:05,880
How long has Wang Mingzhong

693
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:09,390
been captured by No. 90?

694
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:11,710
Yizhong.

695
00:39:12,600 --> 00:39:13,550
It's a good thing.

696
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:15,350
Dried pork from Shengchunyang.

697
00:39:15,550 --> 00:39:16,680
You bought it for me?

698
00:39:16,810 --> 00:39:17,600
I didn't buy it.

699
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:19,530
This is a treat from Captain Zhang.

700
00:39:20,850 --> 00:39:23,390
I heard they caught a big shot last night.

701
00:39:23,550 --> 00:39:24,230
Who is it?

702
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:26,270
I don't know.

703
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,490
Is it a man or a woman?

704
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:31,910
If you want to know,

705
00:39:31,910 --> 00:39:33,310
I can go inquire about it.

706
00:39:34,150 --> 00:39:34,920
No need.

707
00:39:36,190 --> 00:39:37,530
Let's not interfere in

708
00:39:37,790 --> 00:39:39,450
who Captain Zhang has caught.

709
00:40:16,710 --> 00:40:17,510
Director.

710
00:40:25,030 --> 00:40:27,550
This guy is very tough.

711
00:40:27,580 --> 00:40:29,090
He didn't say a word.

712
00:40:29,990 --> 00:40:31,650
Continue the interrogation.

713
00:40:31,900 --> 00:40:33,620
But make sure he doesn't die.

714
00:40:35,430 --> 00:40:36,300
Got it.

715
00:41:33,110 --> 00:41:33,750
Yizhong.

716
00:41:50,010 --> 00:41:52,200
I got important intelligence,

717
00:41:52,350 --> 00:41:54,080
but I don't know who to contact.

718
00:41:56,990 --> 00:41:58,390
The Shanghai Deng troops

719
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:01,200
have urgently redeployed a battalion

720
00:42:01,390 --> 00:42:02,950
to reinforce the Kobayashi Division.

721
00:42:02,950 --> 00:42:05,880
They plan to disarm Commander Luo Wuqiang's forces.

722
00:42:06,270 --> 00:42:07,930
The codename is "the Wu Plan."

723
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:11,310
It looks like the Japanese intend to cut off our support.

724
00:42:11,310 --> 00:42:14,370
They plan to launch the attack early tomorrow morning.

725
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:16,800
If Commander Luo cannot return in time,

726
00:42:17,120 --> 00:42:18,940
leaving the troops without a leader,

727
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:21,200
the consequences will be unimaginable.

728
00:42:22,430 --> 00:42:23,870
This is detailed intelligence.

729
00:42:23,870 --> 00:42:24,710
Take it to him

730
00:42:24,860 --> 00:42:25,170
[New Land]

731
00:42:25,050 --> 00:42:27,710
and tell him to leave Suzhou as soon as possible.

732
00:42:29,260 --> 00:42:29,830
Got it.

733
00:42:30,380 --> 00:42:32,210
[New Land]
